node.content: ["Britain's Prince Andrew has been stripped of royal patronages and military affiliations \u2014 with the queen's approval \u2014 a day after a U.S. district judge rejected his motion to dismiss a lawsuit brought by Virginia Giuffre that alleges he sexually abused her when she was 17.\u00a0", "\"The Duke of York will continue not to undertake any public duties and is defending this case as a private citizen,\" a Buckingham Palace spokesperson said Thursday.", "This story is developing and will be updated.", "For Breaking News & Analysis Download the Free CBS News app"]
